  PLACEHOLDER LICENSE FILE — Phase 4 bootstrap.

  Hummingbird is intended to be released under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  This placeholder records that intent so the repository has an unambiguous
  license from its first commit. Before the first public release, replace this
  file with the full, verbatim Apache-2.0 text (including the appendix and the
  copyright line below) and add SPDX headers to source files:

      SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0

  Rationale:
    - Apache-2.0 matches the license of Colibrì, the reference project whose
      ideas Hummingbird adapts, keeping attribution and reuse compatible.
    - It grants an explicit patent license, which suits a systems runtime that
      may implement patented techniques.

